    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;about-sewsonia&#34;&gt;About SewSonia&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My goal is to help you feel and look your best with personalized bridal and formalwear alterations. As a dedicated seamstress with a passion for craftsmanship and detail, I specialize in creating fit-for-you tailored gowns, and personalized alterations that celebrate your unique style and silhouette.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;my-story&#34;&gt;My Story&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;It all started with a handmade skirt and a little fashion show competition at 10 years old to start my love for sewing garments. Now 25 years later I’ve become obsessed with ball gowns. I found bridal wear to be the most fantastic. Something about making someone feel that princess moment on one of the most magical days of their life is so special..&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Contact</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/contact/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/contact/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;contact&#34;&gt;Contact&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;d love to hear about your vision for your special day or event. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re interested in a custom design, need alterations, or just have questions about my services, please don&amp;rsquo;t hesitate to reach out.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;consultation-requests&#34;&gt;Consultation Requests&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To schedule a consultation, please fill out the form below. Initial consultations are $25 (applied to your service when booked) and typically last about 30-90 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;form action=&#34;https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID&#34; method=&#34;POST&#34; class=&#34;contact-form&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;name&#34;&gt;Full Name *&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;input type=&#34;text&#34; id=&#34;name&#34; name=&#34;name&#34; required&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;email&#34;&gt;Email Address *&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;input type=&#34;email&#34; id=&#34;email&#34; name=&#34;_replyto&#34; required&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;phone&#34;&gt;Phone Number&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;input type=&#34;tel&#34; id=&#34;phone&#34; name=&#34;phone&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;service&#34;&gt;Interested In *&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;select id=&#34;service&#34; name=&#34;service&#34; required&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;&#34;&gt;Please select...&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Custom Bridal Gown&#34;&gt;Custom Bridal Gown&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Bridal Alterations&#34;&gt;Bridal Alterations&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Custom Formalwear&#34;&gt;Custom Formalwear&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Formalwear Alterations&#34;&gt;Formalwear Alterations&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Bridal Party Services&#34;&gt;Bridal Party Services&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;option value=&#34;Other&#34;&gt;Other&lt;/option&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/select&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;event-date&#34;&gt;Event Date (if applicable)&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;input type=&#34;date&#34; id=&#34;event-date&#34; name=&#34;event-date&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;message&#34;&gt;Your Message *&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;textarea id=&#34;message&#34; name=&#34;message&#34; rows=&#34;6&#34; required&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-group&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;label for=&#34;referral&#34;&gt;How did you hear about us?&lt;/label&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;input type=&#34;text&#34; id=&#34;referral&#34; name=&#34;referral&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;input type=&#34;text&#34; name=&#34;_gotcha&#34; style=&#34;display:none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;form-actions&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;button type=&#34;submit&#34; class=&#34;btn btn-primary&#34;&gt;Send Message&lt;/button&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/form&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fitting Hours:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Tuesday - Thursday: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Services</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/services/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/services/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;services&#34;&gt;Services&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;At SewSonia, I offer a comprehensive range of services to ensure you look and feel your absolute best for your special day or formal event.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;custom-alterations&#34;&gt;Custom Alterations&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Bring your dreams into reality with expert alterations to make your wedding dress fit you perfectly.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- - **Comprehensive Alterations**: Including bodice adjustments, hem alterations, bustle addition, and structural changes&#xD;&#xA;- **Minor Alterations**: Strap adjustments, simple hems, and minor fitting issues --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Timeline&lt;/strong&gt;: 6-8 weeks depending on your needs&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- - **Price Range**: Starting at $xxx-$yyy, based on assessment of required alterations --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;!-- ## Formalwear &amp; Special Occasion&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Custom-designed dresses and alterations for all your special events.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- **Custom Formal Dresses**: Evening gowns, prom dresses, mother-of-the-bride and mother-of-the-groom dresses&#xD;&#xA;- **Formal Menswear**: Custom vests, ties, and accessories to coordinate with bridal party&#xD;&#xA;- **Alterations**: Expert alterations on store-bought formal attire&#xD;&#xA;- **Timeline**: 3-4 months recommended for custom pieces&#xD;&#xA;- **Price Range**: Starting at $xxx-$yyy for custom pieces, alteration pricing based on assessment&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## Bridal Party Services&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Ensure your entire bridal party looks cohesive and feels comfortable.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- **Bridesmaid Dresses**: Custom designs or alterations&#xD;&#xA;- **Flower Girl Dresses**: Custom creation or modifications&#xD;&#xA;- **Coordinating Accessories**: Veils, sashes, and pocket squares&#xD;&#xA;- **Group Booking**: Special pricing available for full bridal party services&#xD;&#xA;- **Timeline**: 3-4 months recommended&#xD;&#xA;- **Pricing**: Varies based on services required&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;## Consultations&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Schedule a consultation to discuss your vision and explore how I can help create your perfect look.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;- **Initial Consultation**: 30-90 minute appointment to discuss needs and options&#xD;&#xA;- **Pricing**: $25 initial consultation fee (applied to final service cost when booked)&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;To schedule a consultation or inquire about services, please [contact me](/contact/). --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;consultations&#34;&gt;Consultations&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Schedule a consultation to discuss your vision and explore how I can help create your perfect fit&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
